name: Triple Cord Infinity Bracelet
description:
Following in the footsteps of the hugely successful double cord Infinity Bracelet, first introduced in the Summer, we are pleased to introduce the NEW triple cord Infinity Bracelet. 

This lovingly hand crafted bracelet looks eye catching worn alone or even better stacked with others, in this autumn/winters hottest colour combinations.

The infinity symbol refers to something 'without any limits' so wear yours as a symbol that anything is possible, the only person holding you back is yourself, live without limits!

The bracelet itself measures 15cms in length with an extension chain giving you another 7cms, so one size fits all

Choose from either gold or silver chain and connectors

In this listing choose from; 

- Mustard (gold/silver)

or

- Navy (gold/silver)


*Please see our other listings for other great colour combinations

name: Vickie Satchel Medium - Yellow
description:
Introducing the latest Satchel to the A New Moda Autumn/Winter 13 collection, the 'Vickie' Satchel is the perfect go to bag for fall, and best of all it comes in 10 different colours so you can match it to your favourite colour palette.

This roomy and versatile satchel comes in two sizes, large and medium. 

Large measurements: 28cm high x 16cm deep x 32cm wide (strap is adjustable)

Medium measurements: 21cm high x 12cm deep x 31cm wide (strap is adjustable)

The interior is a beautiful silver flower print and has a zipped pocket at the back and an open compartment at the from, handy for storing documents, phone, purse.

The Vickie Satchel comes in two options, plain (as seen in the photographs or hand customised with stud work of your choice and design.

Please see photo 5 for choice of studs available. Once purchased, we will be in touch via email to discuss your customisation options. 

**Please allow 5-7 working days for customisation** 

**Note the main image shown here is the large size. All others images are the medium**

IMPORTANT! - there is only 1 of each colour available so don't miss out

name: 'Be Brave' Grace Satchel (hand customised) - Caramel & Chocolate
description:
This seasons must have satchel has now been taken to a whole new level with A New Moda's hand customised Grace Satchel. 

No two are ever the same, individual and unique stud work is added to each bag, and as if that wasn't enough they all get their very own hand painted, original pen and ink artwork added to the perspex window. 

I want your Grace Satchel to inspire you to be brave, take chances and live life to the fullest. The 'be brave' heart is there as a reminder that the only person holding you back is yourself!

'Pen and Ink' work is the traditional process of using a quill or nib dipped in ink and used to draw instead of using a pen. 

To ensure the artwork is as fade resistant as possible I also use coloured acrylic paint to ensure you can go on enjoying your one of kind satchel for years to come. The artwork is also protected in a plastic film, just in case you and your satchel ever get caught in a good old British downpour! 

Now for the boring stuff... Measurements: 34x10x25cm.

Each Grace Satchel comes with a long detachable handle that clips onto either end to turn it into a shoulder bag and to keep it protected when you're not both out on the town, it's got a lovely little dust bag.
